Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest queue cancel

Purpose:
  Cancel one active job.

Usage:
  spinedigest queue cancel <job-id>

Arguments:
  <job-id>              Full job id or an unambiguous prefix.

Behavior:
  - Canceled jobs become terminal history.
  - Their workspace is retained for debugging until `queue clean` removes old retained files.

Example:
  spinedigest queue cancel 75d12f7e
